            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">22.1309</ph> Actions because of noncompliance.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <p id="d1455e13" class="- topic/p ">The contracting officer must take necessary action as soon as possible upon notification by the appropriate agency official to implement any sanctions imposed on a contractor by the Department of Labor for violations of the clause at <ph class="- topic/ph ">
					          <xref href="FAR-i1056230.dita#i1056230"
                     base="i1056230"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">52.222-35</xref>
				        </ph>, Equal Opportunity for Veterans. These sanctions (see 41 CFR 60-300.66) may include-</p>
			      <ol id="d1441e22" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1455e26" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Withholding progress payments;</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1455e35" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Termination or suspension of the contract; or</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1455e44" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Debarment of the contractor.</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
		    </conbody>
